<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='291000' id='t-291000'>for those ancient Polynesian mariners</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='293000' id='t-293000'>that were traversing the Pacific so widely.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='296000' id='t-296000'>But we got up there,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='298000' id='t-298000'>and I had the unique and wonderful scientific opportunity and personal opportunity</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='301000' id='t-301000'>to get to a place that had never been dived</span>
