<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='407000' id='t-407000'>And what's the context of the Phoenix Islands?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='409000' id='t-409000'>Where do these exist?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='411000' id='t-411000'>Well they exist in the Republic of Kiribati,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='413000' id='t-413000'>and Kiribati is located in the Central Pacific</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='415000' id='t-415000'>in three island groups.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='418000' id='t-418000'>In the west we have the Gilbert Islands.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='420000' id='t-420000'>In the center we have the Phoenix Islands,</span>
