<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:05
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='474000' id='t-474000'>They're also a country</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='476000' id='t-476000'>that is in dire danger.</span>
