<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:58
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='527000' id='t-527000'>After I got back, I said,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='529000' id='t-529000'>okay, this is amazing, what we found.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='531000' id='t-531000'>I'd like to go back and share it with the government of Kiribati,</span>
