<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='536000' id='t-536000'>the westernmost group.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='538000' id='t-538000'>So I started contacting them --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='540000' id='t-540000'>because they had actually given me a permit to do this --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='542000' id='t-542000'>and I said, &quot;I want to come up and tell you what we found.&quot;</span>
