<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='554000' id='t-554000'>for everybody who comes to the seminar.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='556000' id='t-556000'>So I said, &quot;Okay, I'm happy to buy lunch.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='558000' id='t-558000'>Just get whatever anybody wants.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='560000' id='t-560000'>So David Obura, a coral reef biologist, and I went to Tarawa,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='563000' id='t-563000'>and we presented for two hours</span>
