<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='567000' id='t-567000'>And the country never knew this. They never had any data from this area.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='570000' id='t-570000'>They'd never had any information from the Phoenix Islands.</span>
