<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='719000' id='t-719000'>the government of New Zealand, the World Bank.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='721000' id='t-721000'>The Oak Foundation and National Geographic</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='723000' id='t-723000'>have been big funders of this as well.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='725000' id='t-725000'>And we basically founded the park</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='727000' id='t-727000'>on the idea of an endowment</span>
